sourcesContent:
import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Stepper,
  Step,
  StepLabel,
  StepContent,
} from '@mui/material';
import CloudUploadIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CloudUpload';
import SettingsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Settings';
import CheckCircleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CheckCircle';

const HowItWorks = () => {
  const steps = [
    {
      label: 'Upload Your Video',
      description: 'Simply drag and drop your video file or click to browse. We support all major video formats.',
      icon: <CloudUploadIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />
    },
    {
      label: 'Video Processing',
      description: 'Advanced AI-powered video processing to detect traffic signs and alerts.',
      icon: <SettingsIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />
    },
    {
      label: 'Get Results',
      description: 'Receive your processed video with detailed analytics and download options.',
      icon: <CheckCircleIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />
    }
  ];

  return (
    <Box>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box sx={{ 
        color: 'white', 
        py: 12,
        position: 'relative',
        '&::before': {
          content: '""',
          position: 'absolute',
          top: 0,
          left: 0,
          right: 0,
          bottom: 0,
          backgroundImage: 'url("/settings.jpg")',
          backgroundSize: 'cover',
          backgroundPosition: 'center',
          backgroundRepeat: 'no-repeat',
          zIndex: -2,
        },
        '&::after': {
          content: '""',
          position: 'absolute',
          top: 0,
          left: 0,
          right: 0,
          bottom: 0,
          backgroundColor: 'rgba(46, 39, 39, 0.7)', // primary color with opacity
          zIndex: -1,
        }
      }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ position: 'relative', zIndex: 1 }}>
          <Typography 
            variant="h2" 
            component="h1" 
            textAlign="center" 
            gutterBottom
            sx={{ 
              textShadow: '2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)',
              fontWeight: 'bold'
            }}
          >
            How It Works
          </Typography>
          <Typography 
            variant="h5" 
            textAlign="center" 
            sx={{ 
              mb: 4, 
              maxWidth: '800px', 
              mx: 'auto',
              textShadow: '1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)'
            }}
          >
            Our simple three-step process makes video processing effortless
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Process Steps */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Box sx={{ py: 8 }}>
          <Grid container spacing={4}>
            {steps.map((step, index) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} md={4} key={index}>
                <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
                  <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', py: 4 }}>
                    <Box sx={{ color: 'primary.main', mb: 2 }}>
                      {step.icon}
                    </Box>
                    <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                      {step.label}
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography color="text.secondary">
                      {step.description}
                    </Typography>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Box>
      </Container>

      {/* Detailed Process Section */}
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'grey.50', py: 8 }}>
        <Container maxWidth="md">
          <Typography variant="h3" textAlign="center" gutterBottom>
            Detailed Process
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" textAlign="center" sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
            Learn more about each step of our video processing workflow
          </Typography>
          
          <Stepper orientation="vertical">
            <Step active>
              <StepLabel>
                <Typography variant="h6">1. Upload Your Video</Typography>
              </StepLabel>
              <StepContent>
                <Typography paragraph>
                  Start by uploading your video file to our secure platform. We support a wide range of formats including:
                </Typography>
                <Box component="ul" sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                  <Typography component="li">MP4, AVI, MOV</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">WebM, MKV</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">FLV, WMV</Typography>
                </Box>
              </StepContent>
            </Step>
            
            <Step active>
              <StepLabel>
                <Typography variant="h6">2. Configure Processing Options</Typography>
              </StepLabel>
              <StepContent>
                <Typography paragraph>
                  Choose from our extensive range of processing options:
                </Typography>
                <Box component="ul" sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                  <Typography component="li">Resolution adjustment</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">Format conversion</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">Custom filters and effects</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">Compression settings</Typography>
                </Box>
              </StepContent>
            </Step>
            
            <Step active>
              <StepLabel>
                <Typography variant="h6">3. Process and Download</Typography>
              </StepLabel>
              <StepContent>
                <Typography paragraph>
                  Our system will process your video according to your specifications. Once complete, you can:
                </Typography>
                <Box component="ul" sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                  <Typography component="li">Preview the processed video</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">Download in your preferred format</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">View processing analytics</Typography>
                  <Typography component="li">Share directly with others</Typography>
                </Box>
              </StepContent>
            </Step>
          </Stepper>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default HowItWorks;
